videos.headline: Kent State cuts Buffalo's lead on 41-yard TD
videos.description: Dustin Crum completes a pass to Xavier Williams who navigates 41 yards to the end zone to score a Kent State touchdown to cut the Buffalo lead to 27-20.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kent State cuts Buffalo's lead on 41-yard TD) 2019/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kent State ties it up on Carrigan's TD
videos.description: Dustin Crum completes a short pass to Mike Carrigan to score a five-yard Kent State touchdown to tie Buffalo at 27-27.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kent State ties it up on Carrigan's TD) 2019/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kent State secures comeback win with last second FG
videos.description: Matthew Trickett nails a 44-yard field goal to seal a 30-27 comeback victory for Kent State over Buffalo.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kent State secures comeback win with last second FG) 2019/11/14 ESHEET
